### Login
// @name login
POST {{authUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=admin&password=p

### Login mit falschem Passwort
// @name login
POST {{authUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=admin&password=FALSCH

### Vorhandenes Lied aktualisieren
PUT {{restUrl}}/2
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}
If-Match: "0"

< .\json\lied-put.json

### NICHT-Vorhandenes Lied aktualisieren
PUT {{restUrl}}/999999
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}
If-Match: "0"

< .\json\lied-put.json

### Vorhandenes Lied *OHNE* Versionsnummer aktualisieren
PUT {{restUrl}}/2
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}

< .\json\lied-put.json

### Vorhandenes Lied mit falscher Versionsnummer aktualisieren
PUT {{restUrl}}/2
Content-Type: application/json
If-Match: 0
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}

< .\json\lied-put.json

### Vorhandenes Lied mit alter Versionsnummer aktualisieren
PUT {{restUrl}}/2
Content-Type: application/json
If-Match: "-1"
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}

< .\json\lied-put.json

### Vorhandenes Lied mit ungueltigen Daten aktualisieren
PUT {{restUrl}}/2
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}
If-Match: "0"

< .\json\lied-put-invalid.json
